Interface VelocityAccess.QueryStringUtilConstants

  • Enclosing interface:
    VelocityAccess

    public static interface VelocityAccess.QueryStringUtilConstants
    Get methods for accessing field constants defined in QueryStringUtil.

    The sole purpose of this interface is to provide access to QueryStringUtil constants in Velocity, e.g: $queryStringUtil.MATCH_ALL_QUERY
